body_html: We generally use the default of clang for OS X compilation, which explains your error. When I run gcc --version I get Apple LLVM version 7.0.2 (clang-700.1.81). You should try switching to clang instead of gcc, since that's the supported approach.

body: We generally use the default of clang for OS X compilation, which explains your error. When I run `gcc --version` I get `Apple LLVM version 7.0.2 (clang-700.1.81)`. You should try switching to clang instead of gcc, since that's the supported approach.
